						</div>
						<div class="hidden sm:flex items-center xl:ml-32 xl:mr-4">
							<div class="flex gap-2 items-center text-gray-100 xl:scale-150">
								<i>
									<svg
										xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
										width="23"
